<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Updates - Cqolin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
    <style>
      .updates-container {
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px;
        background-color: black;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .updates-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .updates-list li {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 10px auto;
        padding: 15px;
        width: 80%;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
      }
      .updates-list li h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .updates-list li p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .back-button {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        left: 20px;
        background-color: #1e90ff;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 50%;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        font-size: 20px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }
      .back-button:hover {
        background-color: #00bfff;
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }
      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(-20px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <button class="back-button" onclick="window.location.href='/home';">
      &#9664;
    </button>
    <div class="updates-container">
      <h1>Updates</h1>
      <ul class="updates-list">
        <li>
          <h2>New Feature: Improved Link Management</h2>
          <p>
            We have enhanced the link management system with better organization
            and categorization features.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>Bug Fix: Link Thumbnail Issue</h2>
          <p>Fixed the issue with link thumbnails not displaying correctly.</p>
        </li>
        <!-- Add more updates as needed -->
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
